## Component Checklist Before Submitting

- [ ] Component has proper TypeScript types
- [ ] All props have default values via `withDefaults`
- [ ] Events are properly typed with `defineEmits`
- [ ] Component is exported from `src/index.ts`
- [ ] Storybook story exists and covers all variants
- [ ] Storybook play function includes accessibility tests
- [ ] Unit tests exist and pass
- [ ] Component builds without errors (`pnpm build`)
- [ ] Linting passes (`nx run {component}:lint`)
